title: Wanna start an OCE Team!
body:
Hey, im currently S1 and was wondering if anyone in OCE wanted to start duoing or even making a team?
would be fun... I play JG and AD, however i can play pretty much any role :)

replies.body:
Hey man, i just added you, we can start a team together 
IGN: HungLowe
yea sweet, we can start duoing soon :)
Would be interested, but not sure if you'd think I'm good enough. I mainly play Evelynn in the Jungle, but can also play Annie Mid and Eve & Annie Top.
hey man, just try get out of Bronze first. Best of luck :)
